description:
This is a 22 minute workout called 'Beginner Hip Hop Indoor Cycling Class | 20 Minute' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Nightclub Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Welcome to my first themed beginner indoor cycling workout! It's all hip hop today for 20 minutes!
